 Reiki (pronounced Ray-Key) is a natural healing method designed by Dr Mikao Usui. Reiki is the Japanese word meaning 'Universal Life-Force-Energy'. This album comprises an hour of very chilled music: traditional acoustic instruments such as flute and guitar delicately overlay soothingly warm synthesizer chords to create a selection of gentle musical landscapes.
"The 12 tracks are each about five minutes in length and so are suitable for a general Reiki treatment, either working on the seven chakras or the more traditional 12 hand positions. The album is also great for treatments with other complementary therapies or simply meditating." - Darren Yap, Reiki Master
